---
title: Mumbai Chicken & Spiced Potatoes with Mixed Salad & Yoghurt
description: We can't work out which is best: the pop of brown mustard seeds on the roasted potato and fried onion, the gentle
warmth of the spiced chicken or the burst and crunch of the mixed leaf salad. You decide!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
